title: ACTIVISTS, ELITES, & THE LEFT
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: I develop an original account of internal party divides.  Using the 2016 primary, the 2019 UK election, and the Tea Party movement as case studies I try to offer a fresh take on many of the most contentious disagreements we have on the left.
